When a place makes your child’s eyes light up, you know it’s a hit! 🥰

We spent the day at Plaza Playland at @jioworldplaza, and my son Ishaan had the time of his life. He had a sugar rush at the Hamleys Candyland and absolutely loved racing tiny cars on the Hot Wheels Speed Track.

There are 10 unique zones filled with fun and creativity and every corner had something new waiting for us ✨

If you’re looking for something exciting to do indoors during Mumbai rains, this is it.
It’s open daily from 12 PM to 8 PM, until June 3rd.🤍

Go book your tickets now from BookMyShow and thank me later! 🫶🏻
